MEET THE TEAM
Chamber Board of Directors
Board members are elected by the membership. Positions are rotated to maintain consistency. Each is eligible to serve a 3-year term.
President
COREY BRYAN
I'm Corey Bryan and my wife Peggy and I have a little farm called
Turkey Hollow.
We have small events on our property and make crafts that fit the late 1800s for festivals.
We have been Williston Chamber members for three years and I am currently on the board of directors where I work with other members for events and fundraising for the chamber to enhance Willistons small town charm and beauty.
My wife and I are retired and love the farm life and the people in our community. We are crazy about our grandchildren but never seem to get to see them enough. We do enjoy camping when we can get a break from taking care of our farm chores and exploring this great area

WILLISTON
A good place to live, work & play
The Williston Area Chamber of Commerce is dedicated to the promotion of Williston and its businesses.
The all-volunteer Chamber Board of Directors sets the policies of the Chamber, which are carried out
by the executive director - a part time paid position.
